tr_updateDescription: E vai ra te hoê faanahoraa apî no Organized
tr_howToUseApp: E nafea ia faaohipa ia Organized
tr_appAboutDesc:
Ua hamanihia Organized no te mau amuiraa a te mau Ite no Iehova. Ta'na fa, ia ohie e ia vitiviti te mau ohipa faanahonahoraa a te amuiraa e ia maitai atu â te hi'opoaraa i te mau natairaa no te taatoaraa.

Faanaho i te mau pureraa i te ava‘e piti i te hepetoma e te pureraa i te hopearaa hepetoma ma te ohie, tono i te mau parauraa taviniraa, e hi'o i te mau tuhaa i faataahia no oe ma te taumi noa e piti toru taime. Ua hamanihia teie app ia nehenehe te taatoaraa i roto i te amuiraa e faaohipa e e fana'o i te reira.

Te ohipa nei matou ia maitai atu â Organized no te tuu mai i te tahi atu mau ravea apî a muri a'e. E nehenehe oe e tauturu mai ia matou ia matara oioi mai teie mau ravea anaanatae! E nehenehe oe e turu mai na roto i te mau ô aore ra na roto i te tautururaa i te faahoturaa i te mau faanahoraa no a muri a'e o Organized.
tr_wantSupportApp: Te hinaaro ra oe e tauturu ia Organized?
tr_supportAppDesc: E app tamoni ore Organized, e te oaoa nei matou i te faahotu e i te faaite atu i te reira. Noa 'tu e te ohipa nei matou ma te aau tae, e titauhia te moni no te atuaturaa. Mai te peu e te hinaaro ra oe e faaite i to oe mauruuru, e farii popou matou i ta oe tauturu!
tr_supportAppOption1Desc: E tauturu ta oe mau ô ia vai tamoni ore noa Organized no te mau amuiraa. E aufau te reira i te mau haamau'araa o te server e e tauturu ia matou ia hamani oioi i te mau ravea apî. E tauturu to oe aau horoa noa i te mau amuiraa na te ao nei!
tr_supportAppOption2Desc:
E mauruuru matou i ta oe tauturu i roto i te mau tuhaa i muri nei:

  • Faahoturaa React
  • Faanahoraa UI/UX
  • Huri i te reo o te App

Mai te peu e nehenehe ta oe e tauturu i roto i teie mau tuhaa, farerei mai ia matou. Ia ohipa amui tatou no te haamaitai ia Organized!

Hau atu â, te faaiteraa ia Organized ia vetahi ê, e tauturu te reira ia parare e ia fana'o te mau amuiraa. Te mau ravea atoa ta oe e rave no te turu, e haamaitai te reira i te app no te taatoaraa.
tr_themeFollowOSDisable: Tapo i te tauiraa hoho'a aunoa?
tr_themeFollowOSDisableDesc: Mai te peu e te hinaaro ra oe e faaho'i i te hoho'a i nia i te aunoa, e nehenehe e na reira i roto i te mau faanahoraa o ta oe pute
tr_2FATokenInvalidExpired: E ere te code i te mea tano aore ra ua mairi te taime. Tamata faahou na.
tr_searchResults: Mau faahopearaa o te maimiraa: {{ count }}
tr_featureComingSoon: Fatata te ohipa apî i te matara mai
tr_featureComingSoonDesc: Aita teie ravea e vai ra i teie nei. Te ohipa nei matou i nia iho. Faaea noa mai!
tr_enterPIN: Tuu i ta oe code PIN
tr_pinRequired: No te hi'o aore ra no te faatano i teie haamaramaramaraa, a tuu i ta oe code PIN e faaohipahia no te iriti i te app.
tr_changeAccessCodeDesc: Ta matou a'oraa, ia taui i te code mai te peu noa e ua itehia te tahi tomoraa faatia-ore-hia. I muri iho i te hamaniraa i te code apî, a tapao maitai i te reira e a faaite i te mau taata faaohipa apî o Organized i roto i ta oe amuiraa.
tr_changeAccessCode: Taui i te code tomoraa o te amuiraa
tr_currentCode: Code tomoraa o te amuiraa i teie nei
tr_newCode: Code tomoraa apî o te amuiraa
tr_noPersonsFoundDesc: Aita e taata e tuati ra i ta oe maimiraa. Tamata i te faatano i te tuhaa aore ra te taio mahana.
tr_forceRefreshButtonTooltip: Faahou ma te puai i te app no te hi'o i te mau faanahoraa apî mai te peu aita e faaitehia mai ra. Eita te mau haamaramaramaraa e tumâhia.
tr_dateRangeSelectStart: Maiti na mua i te taio mahana haamataraa
tr_noNotificationsDesc: E faaitehia te mau faaararaa faufaa i ǒ nei.
tr_userRoleChangedDesc: Ua tauihia ta oe mau tiaraa tomoraa i roto ia Organized a'enei. Tapio e haamata faahou i roto i ta oe pute ia mana te mau tauiraa.
tr_personHasNoAssignmentHistory: Aita e aamu no te natairaa to teie taata
tr_appUserProfile: Pute a te taata faaohipa App
tr_appUserProfileNotRegisteredDesc: Aita teie taata e faaohipa ra i te app i teie nei. E nehenehe oe e hamani i te hoê pute Organized no teie taata i nia i te api 'Pute a te taata faaohipa'.
tr_appUserProfileRegisteredDesc: Te faaohipa nei teie taata ia Organized. Taime hopea i nia i te Itenati: {{ lastTimeOnline }}. Faatano i te tahi atu mau tiaraa e mau faanahoraa i nia i te api 'Pute a te taata faaohipa'.
tr_manageUserProfileSettings: Faatano i te mau faanahoraa o te pute a te taata faaohipa
tr_createUserProfile: Hamani i te pute a te taata faaohipa
tr_consoleWarningDesc: E mauhaa puai teie no te feia hamani faanahoraa. Mai te peu e ere oe i te taata hamani faanahoraa, eiaha e papai aore ra e pape i te mau faaueraa i ǒ nei – noa 'tu e na te hoê taata i ani atu. Ma te na reira, e vai paruru noa ta oe mau haamaramaramaraa i roto i te app Organized.
tr_offlineLocked: Ia vai te Itenati no te rave i te tauiraa
tr_fillRequiredField: A faaî i te vahi titauhia
